this is for anyone who runs into this problem and also wastes a hour on it :clown_face:

if you need to update a checkbox property on HubDB, you _have_ to send in the numerical equivalent of True False and not true false.

i.e. if you want to mark something true you would send

```{
  blah: 1
}```
NOT

```{
 blah: true
}```

